        <p class="mb-3 text-sm">
          I transform your ideas into effective, optimized landing pages
          designed to capture attention and convert visitors into customers.
        </p>
        <ul class="mb-4 -ml-1 space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-1">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 mt-px text-purple-800"
